{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"00c24eec7e","title":"中共中央关于取消军委办公会议、成立中央军委常委的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac9cfdb8c7","index":0,"year":1975,"month":2,"day":5,"articleId":"00c24eec7e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b0bbbe3e5a","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于取消军委办公会议、成立中央军委常委的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"},{"id":"29039f540d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席已圈阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"},{"id":"57bd0b6992","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）为了加强军队建设和战备工作的领导，毛主席、党中央决定取消军委办公会议，成立中国共产党中央军事委员会常务委员会。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"},{"id":"1d59a218de","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）叶剑英、王洪文、邓小平、张春桥、刘伯承、陈锡联、汪东兴、苏振华、徐向前、聂荣臻、粟裕十一位同志为常务委员。军委常委会由叶剑英同志主持。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"},{"id":"a6721194a5","type":"paragraph","text":"总参谋部第一副总长，总政治部第一副主任，总后勤部党委第一书记，军委办公厅主任列席常委会议。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"},{"id":"37e3bd8030","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）军委党委会是在毛主席、党中央领导下，处理军委日常工作的办事机构。对军内外一律用军委名义，不用军委常委会名义。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e"}],"page":{"id":"249fd1beac","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"00c24eec7e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}